    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei aeterni. <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/21"
                            >Berengarius </persName>divina favente clementia <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >imperator augustus</rs>. Noverit omnium fidelium sancte Dei Ecclesie
                        nostrorumque presentium scilicet ac futurorum industria, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Count #fidelisOf" ref="#people/188">Grimaldum
                            </persName><rs key="#Count">gloriosum comitem</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Marquis/duke #fidelisOf" ref="#people/1502"
                            >Odelricum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">inclitum marchionem</rs> carissimos <rs
                            key="#Intercessory #fidelisOf">fideles nostros humiliter nostram adiisse
                            clementiam</rs>, quatenus quoddam <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >pratum iuris imperii nostri</rs> pertinens <geogName key="#Comitatus"
                            ref="#estates/124"><rs key="#Comitatus">de comitatu Veronensi
                            </rs></geogName><geogName
                            key="#Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Sculdahis #Other_administrative_unit"
                            ref="#estates/182"><placeName
                                key="#Landed_possessions #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Sculdahis #Other_administrative_unit"
                                ref="#places/919"><rs key="#Sculdahis #Other_administrative_unit">de
                                    sculdasia videlicet que Fluvium</rs></placeName></geogName>
                        dicitur <persName key="#Chancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1501"
                            >Iohanni</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor #Bishops">venerabili episcopo et fidelissimo
                            cancellario nostro</rs> proprietario nomine concedere dignaremur, sicut
                        hic inferius mensure et coherentie iuste et legaliter manifestant: cui ab
                        uno capite <rs key="#Boundary_settings #Monasteries">iura <orgName
                                key="#Boundary_settings #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/137"
                                >monasterii Sancte Marie</orgName> adiacent</rs>, ab alio latere <rs
                            key="#Boundary_settings #Consortes/shared_possessions">plures homines
                            habent</rs>, ab alio capite <rs key="#Boundary_settings #Churches"
                                ><orgName key="#Boundary_settings #Churches">ecclesia Sancti
                                Iusti</orgName> possidet</rs>, ab altero latere decurrit <rs
                            key="#Rivers">rivus qui Altanellus</rs> vocatur. habet ipsum pratum in
                        longitudine perticas legittimas nonaginta octo, pedes legittimas sex, ab
                        alio latere in longitudine perticas legittimas nonaginta quattuor, ab uno
                        capite ex transversum perticas legittimas quinquaginta unam, ab alio capite
                        perticas legittimas duas. Quorum precibus acclinati, predictum pratum de
                        prenominato comitatu de sculdasia Fluvio pertmens, sicut hic superius
                        coherentie et mensure declarant et ad nostrum regnum usque ad hos dies
                        peninuit, Iohanni venerabili episcopo et cancellario nostro iure perpetuo
                        per hoc nostrum imperiale preceptum concedimus et largimur, ac de nostro
                        iure et dominio in eius ius et dominium omnino transfundimus ac delegamus ad
                        habendum, tenendum, vendendum, commutandum; alienandum, pro anima iudicandum
                        et quicquid voluerit faciendum, totius potestatis contradictione remota. Si
                        quis igitur hoc nostre concessionis seu donationis preceptum infringere vel
                        violare aliquo modo temptaverit, sciat se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty"
                            >auri optimi libras triginta</rs>, medietatem <rs key="#Camera_regis"
                            >camera nostra</rs> et medietatem predicto Iohanni episcopo aut cui ipse
                        dederit vel habere concesserit. Quod ut verius credatur et diligentius ad
                        omnibus observetur, manu propria roborantes de anulo nostro subter iussimus
                        insigniri. Signum domni (M) Berengarii serenissimi imperatoris. <persName
                            key="#Chaplain"><name ref="Ermefredus">Hermenfredus</name></persName>
                        domni imperatoris <rs key="#Chaplain">capellanus</rs> ipsius imperiali
                        iussione recognovi et subscripsi. Data .XV. kal. ian. , anno dominice
                        incarnationis .DCCCXV ., domni vero Berengarii serenissimi regis .XXVIII.,
                        imperii. autem sui .III., indicione .VI. Actum <placeName ref="#places/59"
                            >Verona</placeName>. in Christi nomine feliciter, amen.</ab>
